00:03:17.250 --> 00:03:20.540
not only a keyboard
player and a cello player.

00:03:20.540 --> 00:03:21.840
He's also a conductor.

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.490
That's what you do.

00:03:23.490 --> 00:03:25.790
&gt;&gt; Jonathan Cohen:
That's right [laughter].

00:03:25.790 --> 00:03:28.780
&gt;&gt; Anne Sofie von Otter:
Maybe more than [inaudible].

00:03:28.780 --> 00:03:32.530
