00:03:32.530 --> 00:03:34.260
And I just love these guys.

00:03:34.260 --> 00:03:35.560
They are so wonderful.

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:39.580
They're really such musicians
and such freedom and so nice.

00:03:39.580 --> 00:03:43.380 position:56%
