00:04:19.960 --> 00:04:21.980
&gt;&gt; Thomas Dunford Duration:
I loved all of them

00:04:21.980 --> 00:04:23.280
and they were all different.

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:24.580
This one was [inaudible].

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:30.470
