You mean when I do other
recitals with Nordic music?

00:05:36.180 --> 00:05:37.930
&gt;&gt; Nicholas Brown: Yeah.

00:05:37.930 --> 00:05:39.970
&gt;&gt; Anne Sofie von Otter:
Well, Nordic music,

00:05:39.970 --> 00:05:43.770
a lot of it is extremely
beautiful and has a certain --

00:05:43.770 --> 00:05:46.330
its own character and
the text and everything.

00:05:46.330 --> 00:05:48.750
Of course, Swedish
is my own language,

00:05:48.750 --> 00:05:50.750
but the songs are exceptionally
good.

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:55.060
Grieg, the Norwegian
composer, Grieg, Sibelius.

