00:18:07.370 --> 00:18:08.670
&gt;&gt; Anne Sofie von Otter:
Music education

00:18:08.670 --> 00:18:10.490
in Sweden is terrible [laughter].

00:18:10.490 --> 00:18:15.340
It really, really is.

00:18:15.340 --> 00:18:21.910
I mean at least, if you're
thinking classical music,

00:18:21.910 --> 00:18:27.360
musical education [inaudible]
in a broader sense why this is.

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:31.050
