rigid about the way of learning

00:19:56.500 --> 00:19:58.040
about -- this is harmony.

00:19:58.040 --> 00:20:03.280
You have to learn four, four
and three, three, and you forget

00:20:03.280 --> 00:20:05.780
about five, seven,
Indian music, jazz,

00:20:05.780 --> 00:20:07.080
improvisation, and all this stuff.

00:20:07.080 --> 00:20:09.830
And they tend to have
this thing of schools.

00:20:09.830 --> 00:20:11.130
We are the best school.

00:20:11.130 --> 00:20:13.240
You have to stay in
school and study here.

00:20:13.240 --> 00:20:18.160
But actually music -- the best
experiences is playing with people.

00:20:18.160 --> 00:20:20.640
And that's how I learned even more.

00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:22.050
It's good for giving a basis,

00:20:22.050 --> 00:20:25.140
